443    /**
444    * Replace duplicate exits in control structures. If the node following
445    * the exit node expression has the same effect as exit node, the node can
446    * be replaced or removed.
447    * For example:
448    * "while (a) {return f()} return f();" ==> "while (a) {break} return f();"
